# oops_Tree — Production-Grade Financial Research Agent Upgrade

Upgrade the existing oops_Tree equity research pipeline from a linear LangGraph workflow with a single LLM to a production-grade, decision-ready financial analysis engine with dual-model routing, persistent hybrid vector search, cyclical agent reflection, deterministic quantitative tools, and confidence-weighted investment memos.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **GLM-4.7 Cloud API Key**: You'll need a Zhipu AI / Z.ai API key added to [.env](file:///c:/Users/Asus/Downloads/ops_Tree/oops_Tree/.env) as `ZHIPU_API_KEY`. The GLM-4.7 API uses an OpenAI-compatible endpoint (`https://open.bigmodel.cn/api/paas/v4/`). Confirm you have access.

> [!WARNING]
> **Qdrant storage change**: Switching from `:memory:` to persistent `./db` path. Existing in-memory data will not carry over — re-ingestion will happen on first run. This is a one-time migration.

> [!CAUTION]
> **Python REPL tool**: The DCF/WACC node executes Python code generated by the LLM inside a sandboxed `exec()` with restricted builtins. This is standard for LangGraph financial agents but should be reviewed for your deployment context.

---

## Gap Analysis: What Exists vs. What's Needed

| Feature | Current State | Target State |
|---|---|---|
| **LLM Routing** | Single model: Groq `llama-3.1-8b-instant` for all tasks | **Quick**: Groq `llama-3.3-70b-versatile` · **Deep**: GLM-4.7 Cloud |
| **Qdrant Storage** | In-memory (`:memory:`) — lost on restart | Persistent `./db` path — zero-cost, private |
| **Vector Retrieval** | Dense vectors only (`all-MiniLM-L6-v2`) | **Hybrid**: Dense + Sparse (BM25) vectors |
| **Metadata Grounding** | Basic ticker+year filter | Hard filters: Ticker, Fiscal Year, Document Type |
| **Reflection Node** | None — linear flow | Senior Analyst reviews output for contradictions/hallucinations |
| **Quantitative Tools** | None — LLM guesses math | Python REPL executes DCF, WACC deterministically |
| **Output Format** | Basic JSON report | Structured investment memo with confidence scores + citations |
| **Frontend** | Streamlit UI (good) | Add DCF results, confidence scores, citations, reflection status |

